name: Low Life
description: Accept it, life is cruel and unfair. But hey, it is cruel and unfair to everyone; and that is exactly what makes it fair. They say some people have humble beginnings; we can't say the same for what reflects the life of Low Life though. She woke up in an orphanage, with just a little number and a pair of old clothes to her name, leaving her to figure her way out of a mess she never voluntarily walked into. What she first learned as she entered her teenage years was how to create a deadly shiv, followed by hacking into the orphanage data networks to get her 'adopted' by a fictional family, throwing herself face-first into a dystopian world of crime and violence, one she managed to naturally excel against.
